text: Babenhausen is a municipality in Unterallgäu in Bavaria, Germany. It is seat of a municipal association with Egg an der Günz, Kettershausen, Kirchhaslach, Oberschönegg and Winterrieden. ==References== == Other websites == * * Fugger – official Fugger family website with information on the museum in Babenhausen (in German) Category:Unterallgäu
title: Babenhausen, Bavaria
